external_knowledge:
Active weather stations refer to stations with a status of 'active' and have collected data within the last year; 
The 'average temperature' is calculated based on the actual values collected by the weather stations for the data type 'temperature'. 
Latest collection dates are the most recent dates when data was collected for each location.

-last May refers to May 2023 in this context; 
-temperature readings quality is scored based on the quality_score column in the data_quality table;
-average quality is a measure of reliability and usefulness of the temperature data.
